com.ostrichemulators.semtool.ui.preferences

Class StoredMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ostrichemulators.semtool.ui.preferences.StoredMetadata

  • public class StoredMetadata
extends Object
    A class to store data about individual databases (things like graph icons, colors, insight locations, reification data). This class if different from the standard Preferences object in that it is intended for per-database settings instead of UI-specific user preferences.
    Author:
    ryan
